Sentencas: We have been researching Solid oxide fuel cells (SOFCs) with Cu-CeO2-ScSZ (scandia stabilized zirconia) anodes operating directly on ethanol fuels in recent years.
Titulo: Research of carbon deposition formation and judgment in Cu-CeO2-ScSZ anodes for direct ethanol solid oxide fuel cells

Sentencas: In this paper, Cu-CeO2-ScSZ anodes with different Cu/CeO2 composition are fabricated by dry pressing, sintering and wet impregnation technologies.
Titulo: Research of carbon deposition formation and judgment in Cu-CeO2-ScSZ anodes for direct ethanol solid oxide fuel cells

Sentencas: The photographs and SEM images of these samples after exposure to ethanol fuels for 300 h are observed to characterize their carbon deposition behaviors.
Titulo: Research of carbon deposition formation and judgment in Cu-CeO2-ScSZ anodes for direct ethanol solid oxide fuel cells

Sentencas: The different deposited carbon morphologies in the anodes with different compositions are recorded, and possible reaction mechanisms and prevention methods are discussed.
Titulo: Research of carbon deposition formation and judgment in Cu-CeO2-ScSZ anodes for direct ethanol solid oxide fuel cells

Sentencas: Based on these results; we demonstrate the carbon deposition behaviors and degradation reasons for the single cell running in ethanol fuels.
Titulo: Research of carbon deposition formation and judgment in Cu-CeO2-ScSZ anodes for direct ethanol solid oxide fuel cells
